**Key Constants:**
- Mars exterior temp: ranges from -110°C (163K) to +20°C (293K), daily swings of ~100K
- Human metabolic heat: ~100W per person  
- Aerogel U-value: ~0.11 W/m²K (from R-10.3 per inch = R-10.3 × 5.678 = R-58.5 m²K/W, so U = 1/58.5 = 0.017 W/m²K for 1 inch, or ~0.11 W/m²K for reasonable wall thickness)
- Stefan-Boltzmann constant: σ = 5.67e-8 W/m²K⁴

